using it in a video, you should be good. mr.bumpy apparently didnt care (as few really do) otherwise he would have changed the credits to include his name, as-well as Ivo's Though if you want to re-distribute i would suggest including his name somewhere on the page <img src="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" /><br />in reality most people dont care to much about copyright usage, aslong as your not trying to make money directly off there work (IE creating a commercial product, and bundling the skins with it)<br />the absolute worst that would happen, is you get a message from him asking you to stop, and i cant say ive ever seen that happen <img src="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" /><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=62">Jcee</a> — Tue Aug 29, 2017 8:19 pm</p><hr />
