f;"><span style="background-color:#ececec;">? Since it is likely that the skin will be visible certain times when I open the menu.</span></span></span></strong><br /><br /><span style="font-family:Lucida Grande, Trebuchet MS, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color:#ececec;"><span style="color:#323d4f;">I hope your answer, I know that probably is not necessary since the copyright of the skin belongs to </span><span style="color:#800000;"><strong>Ivo</strong></span><span style="color:#323d4f;">, </span></span><span style="color:#323d4f;"><span style="background-color:#ececec;">but I want to make sure. A hug.</span></span></span><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=23425">TamaraJxn</a> — Tue Aug 29, 2017 4:12 pm</p><hr />
